com.interpss.core.algo.dclf

Interface ILineOutageDFactor

  • All Superinterfaces:
    org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier
    All Known Subinterfaces:
    ContingencyAnalysisAlgorithm, NetGenAdjustAlgorithm, SenAnalysisAlgorithm
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    ContingencyAnalysisAlgorithmImpl, NetGenAdjustAlgorithmImpl, SenAnalysisAlgorithmImpl

    public interface ILineOutageDFactor
extends org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject
    A representation of the model object 'ILine Outage DFactor'. Interface of Line Outage Distribution Factor calculation methods for an outage branch and a monitoring branch or all branches in the network. The outage could be OPEN or CLOSE.
    See Also:
    DclfAlgorithmPackage.getILineOutageDFactor()
